/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"930951af36c90ef3a9a01133226509c6520a0244","tid":268981,"uid":93251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T14:28:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>基本上資產放係外國，房署查唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係好多撚多有錢人住公屋, 好憎<br />\n利申 住公屋, 但好窮"},{"pid":"00d161c9c65b4700fcceebca175bba3d93844744","tid":268981,"uid":53798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T14:57:17.000Z","msg":"想做年輕戶主就唔會係正常申請上樓<br />\n<br />\n基本上都係舊戶主轉比你, 當然你都要有戶籍先<br />\n<br />\n簡單講就係你父母將來走左,就可以轉走再留比你"},{"pid":"f52c07e32d6584da4c37df31186e6c0716c59fcf","tid":268981,"uid":77222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T15:45:53.000Z","msg":"死垃圾公屋富戶"},{"pid":"6e666224c3aefc7cf868442cb690c6e9076400fb","tid":268981,"uid":7139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T15:48:10.000Z","msg":"老人排幾耐"},{"pid":"745af92f76d69492278aa13ce80cc8af4aae8800","tid":268981,"uid":118502,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T15:51:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>基本上資產放係外國，房署查唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n擺係大陸都已經得 所以好多支那人都拎到樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我老豆澳門有樓，係香港一樣住公屋，冇問題<br />\nbtw.雖然層樓係我老豆名，但佢阿媽住緊，唔好屌我濫用公屋，所以房署係check 唔到既"},{"pid":"5d5627c46ac9e63226743e37eb8dce51da25bab8","tid":268981,"uid":83913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T16:29:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我21歲開始排單身公屋，上年去房署問，佢話計分個進度，我45歲就有機會到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都係"},{"pid":"7f51edb55ce66008581ad55e1e46398a76b199d5","tid":268981,"uid":83913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T16:30:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但收入點過到<br />\n要炒散炒到40歲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同問<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以到準備派上樓果一年先辭工?"},{"pid":"ec99db89964fd3dc8e2b865811668ad43a7af6bf","tid":268981,"uid":83913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T16:31:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想做年輕戶主就唔會係正常申請上樓<br />\n<br />\n基本上都係舊戶主轉比你, 當然你都要有戶籍先<br />\n<br />\n簡單講就係你父母將來走左,就可以轉走再留比你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n公屋都有世襲制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f059c56b55c184278039d9716cd2d8777c9f4d2d","tid":268981,"uid":83913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T16:32:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老人排幾耐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知，但過咗45歲加50分(好似係"},{"pid":"e3b5dbebe669ec818f74c4cc66d9ac38656c5488","tid":268981,"uid":83913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T16:33:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>基本上資產放係外國，房署查唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n擺係大陸都已經得 所以好多支那人都拎到樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我老豆澳門有樓，係香港一樣住公屋，冇問題<br />\nbtw.雖然層樓係我老豆名，但佢阿媽住緊，唔好屌我濫用公屋，所以房署係check 唔到既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無錯，就算你朋友舉報你都無用<br />\n<br />\n因為我覺得房署根本無權力、資源同人手check外國資產"},{"pid":"c1cf11c5f1ef2c8013ca788de61d7723030bc47d","tid":268981,"uid":7139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T16:35:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>老人排幾耐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知，但過咗45歲加50分(好似係</blockquote><br />\n65歲都要3年 我估"},{"pid":"02bc81966245a367623da092696529f880c42e1d","tid":268981,"uid":4824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T16:38:37.000Z","msg":"我間舊公屋4個人住 係勁細 間得個一間房（阿爸阿媽訓）真係痴撚線 有咩辦法可以有間房？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7489faec81ccdeebc1301e5bcbefc0a46bd6c96b","tid":268981,"uid":77222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T17:40:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我間舊公屋4個人住 係勁細 間得個一間房（阿爸阿媽訓）真係痴撚線 有咩辦法可以有間房？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有 努力搵錢買另一到"},{"pid":"9a796600492048ad4a132f527c0310f1f381caf1","tid":268981,"uid":110964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T17:43:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我間舊公屋4個人住 係勁細 間得個一間房（阿爸阿媽訓）真係痴撚線 有咩辦法可以有間房？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n叫你啊爸啊媽努力生多個出黎，加多個名換大屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbb1f434970eda2a2d125d7866061837db9cb194","tid":268981,"uid":27568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T17:50:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>老人排幾耐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知，但過咗45歲加50分(好似係</blockquote><br />\n65歲都要3年 我估</blockquote><br />\n房署60就算老人<br />\n1~2年就有<br />\n上左公屋無耐,問左D鄰居...<br />\n<br />\n成條邨最多就係老人同新移民<br />\n一係老年新移民...<br />\n之後南亞人..."},{"pid":"bfb5d4da3369c759b4739e6bb2ceddc340c46ef5","tid":268981,"uid":27568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T17:51:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我21歲開始排單身公屋，上年去房署問，佢話計分個進度，我45歲就有機會到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n放心,到時都唔會有<br />\n因為到時都會唔夠單位派<br />\n於是提高個合格分<br />\n<br />\n識人細佬本身就來夠分但就到佢時提高左"},{"pid":"a19efab3c9460325ed5447bcc732eeb00a14500e","tid":268981,"uid":27568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T17:52:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想做年輕戶主就唔會係正常申請上樓<br />\n<br />\n基本上都係舊戶主轉比你, 當然你都要有戶籍先<br />\n<br />\n簡單講就係你父母將來走左,就可以轉走再留比你</blockquote><br />\n一係結婚<br />\n一係公務員<br />\n一係做現金出糧工"},{"pid":"1685857baac2ecd2ce5b2dd1b16c4e89fbd2b95a","tid":268981,"uid":3646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T17:57:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>基本上資產放係外國，房署查唔到<img s